 on the shortwave albedo of clouds (1977) J. Atmos. Sci., 34, pp. 1149-1152","Diner, D.J.; JPL, 4800 Oak Grove Drive, Pasadena, CA 91109, United States; email: djd@jord.jpl.nasa.gov",,,,,,,,00030007,,BAMIA,,"English","Bull. Am. Meteorol. Soc.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-8444229359
